'''Articles of secession''' were official documents that outlined the breakaway of rogue systems. When former [[Jedi Master]] [[Dooku]] gave the [[Raxus Address]]<ref name="Rise">''[[Rise of the Separatists]]''</ref> in [[24 BBY]]<ref name="Date">''[[Rise of the Separatists]]'' places the [[Raxus Address]] two years before the [[First Battle of Geonosis]], dated to [[22 BBY]] by ''[[Star Wars: Timelines]]''.</ref> to denounce the [[Galactic Republic]], beginning the [[Separatist Crisis]], many Rim planets were inspired to leave the Republic. They tendered formal articles of secession and defected to Dooku's [[Confederacy of Independent Systems]]. On one occassion, shortly after the [[Clone Wars]] started, [[Senator]] [[Esu Rotsino]] proclaimed an article of secession and led the entire [[Abrion sector]] in leaving for the Separatists.<ref name="Rise" />

